<m:mspace width="2pt"/>
<m:mi> N </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-62">
Let the vertical displacement be "y". Then, the work done by the net force is :
</para>
<para id="element-63">
