</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-64">
Now, we have values of tension and displacement of the block. Hence, work done by the tension in the string :
</para>
<para id="element-65">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
